Nazley Khan Sharif (amụrụ na 18 Mee 1990) bụ onye ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị South Africa na-eje ozi dị ka osote minista na-ahụ maka ụmụ nwanyị, ndị ntorobịa na ndị nwere nkwarụ na Presidency kemgbe June 2019
A họpụtara Sharif ka ọ bụrụ onye omebe iwu nke mba na ntuli aka nke Mee 2019
Khan bụ onye otu Democratic Alliance
Sharif gụrụ akwụkwọ na Mahadum nke Witwatersrand, ebe ọ gụsịrị akwụkwọ na nzere BA na nzere BA Honours na sayensị ndọrọ ndọrọ ọchịchị.
Mgbe ọ nọ n'afọ mbụ ya na Mahadum nke Witwatersrand, ọ sonyeere Democratic Alliance Students' Organisation (DASO) na campus

Ọ bụ osote onye isi oche maka Nchịkọta na Mgbasa ozi nke DASO, onye isi oche nke DA Youth na mpaghara Johannesburg South nke pati ahụ, onye isi ala nke DA Gauteng South Regional Youth Organisation, na onye isi oche oche nke alaka DASO na Mahadum Wits.
A họpụtara ya dị ka onye kansụl DA na City of Johannesburg Metropolitan Municipality na 2014
A họpụtara Khan ka ọ bụrụ onye zuru ezu n'afọ puku abụọ na iri na isii A họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ onye isi oche nke kọmitii nke ngalaba 79 nke Gender, Youth, and People with Disabilities.

A họpụtara Khan ka ọ bụrụ onye omebe iwu mba na ntuli aka nke Mee 2019. N'ụbọchị nke ise n'ọnwa Juun afọ 2019, a họpụtara ya ka ọ bụrụ osote minista na-ahụ maka ụmụ nwanyị, ndị ntorobịa na ndị nwere nkwarụ n'ọchịchị. Ọ ghọrọ onye otu Portfolio Committee on Women, Youth and People with Disabilities na 27 June 2019.
Na 5 Disemba 2020, a mara ọkwa na Khan ga-anọgide dị ka osote minista na-ahụ maka ụmụ nwanyị, ndị ntorobịa na ndị nwere nkwarụ na onye isi ala na kọmitii na-ahụ anya nke John Steenhuisen duziri.
